  "body": "### Summary\r\nWallet transactions are shown when local notifications are enabled for android and background service is running.\r\nWe should show local notifications of wallet transactions, even when no background service is running (but the app is not killed) and remote notifications are enabled (similar to ios)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\nShow local android notifications for wallet transactions when remote notifications are enabled\r\n\r\n**Original Report**: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/13028#issuecomment-1035523940\r\n**Related comment**: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/13028#issuecomment-1036193464",
